graph TD
    A["User Question<br/>(e.g., Tell me about<br/>my family)"] -->|Check Setting| B["Memory Injection<br/>Enabled?"]

    B -->|No| C["Skip Memory<br/>(LLM answers without<br/>saved facts)"]
    B -->|Yes| D["Retrieve Facts"]

    D --> E["Query Database<br/>(Get facts from 4 sources)"]

    E --> F["Current Facts<br/>(All active facts<br/>from permanent storage)"]

    E --> G["Related by Connections<br/>(Follow relationships)<br/>Example: Find spouse<br/>Find parents<br/>Find co-workers"]

    E --> H["Related by Classification<br/>(Follow type hierarchy)<br/>Example: If ${CHILD1} is a Person,<br/>find all Persons<br/>Find what ${CHILD1} is part of"]

    E --> I["Stored Attributes<br/>(Simple values)<br/>Example: age=12<br/>name=${CHILD1}"]

    F --> J["Similarity Search<br/>(In addition to above,<br/>search vector index<br/>for related memories)<br/>Returns top 10 matches"]
    G --> J
    H --> J
    I --> J

    J --> K["Remove Duplicates<br/>(Same fact mentioned<br/>multiple times?)<br/>Keep the most confident<br/>version)"]

    K --> L["Filter by Context<br/>(Is this relevant to<br/>the question?)<br/>Family query gets<br/>family facts only)"]

    L --> M["Convert to Human Names<br/>(Fact stored as:<br/>8f4c9d2e_uuid to ${SPOUSE})<br/>Replace IDs with<br/>readable names)"]

    M --> N["Attach Aliases<br/>(Include all names<br/>entity knows by)<br/>${SPOUSE} → ${SPOUSE}/${SPOUSE_ALIAS}<br/>Add trust level)"]

    N --> O["Convert to Natural Language<br/>(NOT: (${CHILD1},parent_of,user)<br/>BUT: You are ${CHILD1}'s parent)<br/>Format for human reading)"]

    O --> P["Example Output:<br/>- You are parent of ${CHILD1}<br/>(High confidence)<br/>- ${SPOUSE} is your spouse<br/>(High confidence)<br/>- ${CHILD1} is age 12<br/>(High confidence)<br/>- Has pet named ${PET}<br/>(Pending confirmation)"]

    P --> Q["Add to LLM Context<br/>(Insert before user's<br/>question in message)"]

    Q --> R["LLM Sees Memory Header<br/>(Facts in English<br/>with trust indicators)"]

    R --> S["LLM Generates Response<br/>(Responds using<br/>the memory facts)<br/>Can say: ${CHILD1} is 12<br/>Knows: ${SPOUSE} is spouse"]

    S --> T["User Gets Answer<br/>(Augmented with<br/>saved memories)"]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style P fill:#fff9c4
    style R fill:#f3e5f5
    style S fill:#c8e6c9
    style T fill:#c8e6c9
